how deeply the United States understands Russia's reasonable
concerns, he added.
</P>
<P>
The press secretary said bilateral cooperation between Russia
and the United States will not be affected by the different stands
they hold on the enlargement of NATO and Russia will not beg for
any "philanthropic aid". 
