<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, March 13 (Xinhua) -- The British government is
preparing to evacuate more than 120 British nationals from Albania
in view of the worsening situation there.
</P>
<P>
A British Foreign Office spokesman said in a statement this
afternoon, "In view of the further deterioration of the situation
in Albania and reports that the airport in Tirana is closed, we
are now arranging for evacuation as soon as possible of the more
than 120 British nationals."
</P>
<P>
