and other nationals involved and details are also being broadcast
over the BBC world service," the spokesman said.
</P>
<P>
The spokesman noted that the evacuation would take place either
by military aircraft or by sea. "This is a final warning and there
is no guarantee of any subsequent evacuation being arranged by
civil or military means, he added. 
