international organizations, in particular by the
OSCE(Organization for Security and Cooperation in Europe) and the
European Union, as well as efforts by NATO's individual allies.
</P>
<P>
According to local reports, Albanian President Sali Berisha
called on military intervention by NATO's European allies to calm
the unrest affects most of the country.
</P>
<P>
The Western European Union, the European Union's defense arm,
will meet Friday to consider Berisha's plea for troops, reports
said. 
