The Sudanese and Iranian sides held a round of talks under the
co-chairmanship of the two Foreign Ministers, dealing with the
progress of relations between the two countries.
</P>
<P>
The Iranian Foreign Minister left Khartoum today for Uganda to
resume Iran's good offices to resolve the Sudanese-Ugandan
dispute. 
