<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, March 14 (Xinhua) -- The new generation of China's
collective leadership with Jiang Zemin at the core has the support
of the people of the whole country, Chinese Premier Li Peng said
here this afternoon.
</P>
<P>
Li made the remark during a meeting with Chinese and overseas
journalists shortly after the closing of the Fifth Session of the
Eighth National People's Congress, at the invitation of Zhou Jue,
deputy secretary general and spokesman for the session.
</P>
<P>
"The current session of the National People's Congress, which
had come to a successful conclusion, just approved the report on
the work of the government last year I delivered on behalf of the
State Council. The fifth session of the Eighth National Committee
of the Chinese People's Political Consultative Conference (CPPCC)
also voiced its endorsement to the government work report and its
support to the future work," Li said.
</P>
<P>
