levels are to implement the objectives, goals and measures set
forth in this report and, with the support of the people across
the country, to do still better the work for this year.
</P>
<P>
Our beloved Comrade Deng Xiaoping passed away shortly before
the convocation of the sessions of the NPC and the National
Committee of the CPPCC, and the entire mourning activities,
proceeding in an air of solemnity, were immersed in deepest grief
and held in an orderly way, giving an expression to the people's
profound respects for Deng Xiaoping.
</P>
<P>
Judging from the proceedings of the two sessions of NPC and
CPPCC respectively, we can see that the current collective
leadership with Comrade Jiang Zemin at the core has the support of
the entire Chinese people and China's political situation is
stable.
</P>
<P>
We are convinced that the cause of building socialism with
Chinese characteristics initiated by Comrade Deng Xiaoping is sure
to be carried forward and continue to be developed, and China's
situation will become better and better."
