Vision 2010 Committee that privatization of government-owned
companies is critical to the economic success of the nation, a
spokesman of the committee said on Thursday.
</P>
<P>
Daily Times
</P>
<P>
-- Nigeria expressed hope on Thursday that the Israeli
government would reconsider its decision to construct new housing
units for Jewish settlers in East Jerusalem. 
</P>
