<HEADLINE> Revisions, Supplements Made to Government Work Report (1) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, March 14 (Xinhua) -- Fifteen revisions and supplements
have been made to the Government Work Report delivered by Premier
Li Peng, which was adopted today at the closing meeting of the
Fifth Session of the Eighth National People's Congress.
</P>
<P>
Five of these revisions and supplements are concerned with the
sector of economy, four with science, technology, education and
public health, three with agriculture, two with the building of
democracy, a legal system and a clean and efficient government,
and one with environmental protection.
</P>
<P>
Moreover, some changes and revisions were made in the use of
words and expressions in the report.
</P>
<P>
Two phrases that read "speeding up infrastructural construction
in central and western regions" and "promoting economic
development in central and western regions" were added to a
paragraph that concerns the sustained and fast-speed growth of
national economy.
</P>
<P>
In a relevant paragraph about the contributions of the People's
Liberation Army, armed police force and policemen to the country,
a phrase that reads "support the economic development" was added.
</P>
<P>
According to views of members of the National Committee of the
Chinese People's Political Consultative Conference (CPPCC) from
the science-technology and education circles, one sentence was
added to the contents on the country's existing problems and
contradictions, saying that "science, technology and education
still cannot comply with the demands of the modernization drive."
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> XIE19970314.0188 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-03-14 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Revisions, Supplements Made to Government Work Report (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
On strictly controlling fiscal expenditure, "to strive to
considerably increase the utilization efficiency of funds" was
added.
</P>
<P>
The report turned "strengthening the promotion of socialist
ethical and cultural progress and opening up a new situation in
all aspects of work" into "strengthening the promotion of
socialist ethical and cultural progress and the building of
democracy and a legal system".
</P>
<P>
On building a clean and honest government, requirements that
"officials at or below the county and section level should also
work hard and be clean and honest in performing their duties, and
should consciously subject themselves to supervision and
examination" were added.
</P>
<P>
On easing the financial burden for farmers, the report was
supplemented with "increase of democratic supervision over
financial expenditures at the township and village level". On
poverty-relief work, the report was added with the contents that
"poverty-relief funds must not be diverted for other purposes" and
that "cadres and the masses in the poor areas should strive to
improve their backward conditions through their self-reliant and
hard efforts".
</P>
<P>
On the sector of scientific and technological work, the report
was supplemented with the contents on "continued efforts to run
well national high-tech industrial development zones".
</P>
<P>
In the fields of educational work, words concerning "the
raising of the students' all-round quality", "supporting education
undertakings in poverty-ridden areas" and "reducing the excessive
schoolwork burdens of the primary and middle school students" were
added.
</P>
<P>
With regard to public heath work, the contents on "revitalizing
the science of traditional Chinese medicine and strengthening
medicinal administration" were added.
</P>
<P>
On environmental protection, words of "curbing illegal tree
felling and chopping and wanton mining" were added.
</P>
<P>
In the field of agriculture, there is a supplement "special
attentions" should be paid to guarding against a possible fall in
grain production after a good harvest, to increase in financial
input in agriculture through varied channels, so as to strive for
another good grain crop."
</P>
<P>
Also on agriculture, the contents on "step up building farmland
improvement projects and transforming the low and relatively-low
yield farmland, developing a rural social service network, and
doing grain-storage work still better".
</P>
<P>
On modernization of national defense, the words "due importance
to the development of national defense technology and products"
were replaced by "strengthening national defense sciences
researches, development of technology and the related goods".
</P>
<P>
During the fifth sessions of the NPC and the Eighth National
Committee of the Chinese People's Political Consultative
Conference, the deputies and members spoke highly of the
Government Work Report.
</P>
<P>
The revisions and supplements to this year's government work
report was fewer in number than to any government work report at
preceding sessions over recent years, it is learned.  
</P>
</TEXT>
