<TEXT>
<P>
SANTIAGO, March 13 (Xinhua) -- Chilean acting Minister of
Foreign Affairs Mariano Fernandez held talks today on bilateral
relations with Qian Zhengying, the vice chairman of the Chinese
People's Political Consultative Conference.
</P>
<P>
The two ministers exchanged views on political relations and
economic, commercial cooperation.
</P>
<P>
