partner in Latin America, and China would be the biggest Chilean
copper importer.
</P>
<P>
Chilean Acting Public Works Minister Guillermo Pickering also
held talks with Qian. They analyzed the best ways to use hydraulic
resources.
</P>
<P>
Qian Zhengying, who is also president of the Chinese Red Cross,
later met Zoy Katevas, the president of the Chilean Red
Cross. They discussed the role the Red Cross had played in natural
disasters.
</P>
