Province to help farmers prepare for the spring ploughing.
</P>
<P>
After good grain harvests for two consecutive years, the
Sichuan provincial government decided to increase the agricultural
input in investment, technology, and productive materials.
</P>
<P>
Agricultural departments at all levels organized some 30,000
technicians to go to rural areas, twice the number of technicians
sent last year.
</P>
<P>
