<HEADLINE> Meeting on Women and Sports to Be Held in Cyprus </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NICOSIA, March 13 (Xinhua) -- Around 120 women from all over
Europe is to witness the second "Women and Sports" conference
which is scheduled in Cyprus on March 22.
